"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/388366","Department for Education","false","2015-07-14","<p>The Department for Education does not collect this information. We are funding research which aims to provide firmer information on the numbers and needs of young carers and their families. The research will be completed in spring 2016.</p><p> </p>","Crewe and Nantwich","Edward Timpson",,"2015-07-14T14:16:22.897Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/388366/answer","Biography information for Edward Timpson","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/388366/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/388366/answer",,,,,"60","Education","Education","2015-07-07","Carers: Poverty","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Education, what information her Department collects on poverty levels among young carers.","false","Biography information for Steve McCabe","Birmingham, Selly Oak","Steve McCabe","5800"
